astically improving brand accessibility, functionality, consistency and awareness. Our focus on content strategy, language and visual harmony allowed the simple style to accommodate the diverse audiences with propriety and appeal.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">[scroller]<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-71" src="http://localhost:8888/JoeyGrable.com/2018_wp-grunt/wp-content/uploads/IMG_3094_small.jpg" alt="Capitol Hill Housing community event" /> <img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-90" src="http://localhost:8888/JoeyGrable.com/2018_wp-grunt/wp-content/uploads/IMG_2666-768x1024.jpg" alt="" /> <img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-89" src="http://localhost:8888/JoeyGrable.com/2018_wp-grunt/wp-content/uploads/IMG_2499-1024x768.jpg" alt="" /> <img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-70" src="http://localhost:8888/JoeyGrable.com/2018_wp-grunt/wp-content/uploads/CAPHILLHOUSING-186-1-1024x683.jpg" alt="Ashwin Warrior enters the Capitol Hill Housing offices on 12th Ave." />[/scroller]</span>', 'Capitol Hill Housing Resident Services', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '23-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-07-07 02:31:42', '2018-07-07 02:31:42', '', 23, 'http://localhost:8888/JoeyGrable.com/2018_wp-grunt/23-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
