mittee accepted our proposed marketing plan and the posters, stickers, and postcards were successfully promoted in the Capitol Hill Arts District throughout the summer of 2017.\r\n<h3>Sources</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a href="http://capitolhillarts.org/now-entering/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Capitol Hill Arts, Now Entering campaign</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen-Sans, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif;" href="https://segd.org/what-wayfinding" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Seattle Environmental Graphic Design: What is Wayfinding?</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n[column_wrap count="9"]\r\n<img class="size-thumbnail wp-image-234 alignleft" src="http://localhost:8888/JoeyGrable.com/2018_wp-grunt/wp-content/uploads/CHAD_stickers_4in-dark-150x150.jpg" alt="" />\r\n<img class="size-thumbnail wp-image-227 alignleft" src="http://localhost:8888/JoeyGrable.com/2018_wp-grunt/wp-content/uploads/CHAD_stickers_4in-1-red-150x150.jpg" alt="" />\r\n<img class="size-thumbnail wp-image-228 alignleft" src="http://localhost:8888/JoeyGrable.com/2018_wp-grunt/wp-content/uploads/CHAD_stickers_4in-2-orange-150x150.jpg" alt="" />\r\n<img class="size-thumbnail wp-image-229 alignleft" src="http://localhost:8888/JoeyGrable.com/2018_wp-grunt/wp-content/uploads/CHAD_stickers_4in-3-yellow-150x150.jpg" alt="" />\r\n<img class="size-thumbnail wp-image-230 alignleft" src="http://localhost:8888/JoeyGrable.com/2018_wp-grunt/wp-content/uploads/CHAD_stickers_4in-4-green-150x150.jpg" alt="" />\r\n<img class="size-thumbnail wp-image-231 alignleft" src="http://localhost:8888/JoeyGrable.com/2018_wp-grunt/wp-content/uploads/CHAD_stickers_4in-5-teal-150x150.jpg" alt="" />\r\n<img class="size-thumbnail wp-image-232 alignleft" src="http://localhost:8888/JoeyGrable.com/2018_wp-grunt/wp-content/uploads/CHAD_stickers_4in-6-blue-150x150.jpg" alt="" />\r\n<img class="size-thumbnail wp-image-233 alignleft" src="http://localhost:8888/