ew houses in Photoshop. These renderings where added to project documents and submitted to the local City government and project developers for plan </span>\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">I designed this layout using AutoCAD 2016 for mac. Vice President, Dustin Karami, mentored me through the process of measuring an existing plan at scale, then recreating a top view floor plan using the existing plan data.</span>\n<h3>Sources</h3>\n<ul>\n 	<li><a href="http://sdkatelier.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">SDK Atelier</a></li>\n</ul>', 'SDK Atelier', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '199-autosave-v1', '', '', '2018-07-09 20:52:56', '2018-07-09 20:52:56', '', 199, 'http://localhost:8888/JoeyGrable.com/2018_wp-grunt/199-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
