eated were street-view houses in Photoshop. These renderings where added to project documents, then submitted to project developers and the local City government for design review.</span>\r\n<h3>Sources</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a href="http://sdkatelier.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">SDK Atelier</a></li>\r\n</ul>', 'SDK Atelier', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '199-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-07-09 20:54:06', '2018-07-09 20:54:06', '', 199, 'http://localhost:8888/JoeyGrable.com/2018_wp-grunt/199-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0) ;
