column][column]\r\n<img class="alignnone wp-image-235 size-thumbnail" src="http://localhost:8888/JoeyGrable.com/2018_wp-grunt/wp-content/uploads/CHAD_stickers_4in-light-150x150.jpg" alt="" width="135" height="135" />\r\n[/column]\r\n[/column_wrap]', 'Capitol Hill Arts District', 'As Design Team Lead, some colleagues and I partnered with the Capitol Hill Arts District to design an awareness campaign that coincided with their new website.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '217-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-07-11 19:31:43', '2018-07-11 19:31:43', '', 217, 'http://localhost:8888/JoeyGrable.com/2018_wp-grunt/217-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
