>\r\n</ul>\r\nArchitectural Design Intern\r\n\r\n<em>SDK Atelier | Irvine, CA | Summer 2016</em>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Created digital color schemes and physical mood boards for clients.</li>\r\n 	<li>Rendered house plan elevations in color with landscape and street scenes.</li>\r\n 	<li>Learned how to plot basic floor plans in AutoCAD.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nDigital Designer\r\n\r\n<em>San Onofre Surf Co. | San Clemente, California | July 2013 – September 2016</em>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Coordinated a successful photoshoot for the Fall 2016 girls clothing line.</li>\r\n 	<li>Created graphics and edited pictures for advertisements, banners, products, and special events.</li>\r\n 	<li>Assisted managing the online system for email, e-commerce sales, product management.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nLead Developer\r\n\r\n<em>Beachdude, Inc. | Huntington Beach, California | November 2012 – January 2014</em>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Developed a PayPal integrated e-commerce website application.</li>\r\n 	<li>Re-designed the website to the clients specifications.</li>\r\n 	<li>Integrated a mobile responsive and interactive user interface.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nFreelance Graphic Design\r\n\r\n<em>Self-employed | Lake Forest, CA | July 2012 – 2014</em>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Seattle University Wellness &amp; Health Promotion—designed alcohol awareness poster.</li>\r\n 	<li>nTuple Solutions—produced company logo tailored to the client’s brand identity.</li>\r\n 	<li>Blacklight Fusion band—designed band logo and posters.</li>\r\n 	<li>The Jen &amp; Tonic band—designed band logo.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Skills</h3>\r\n<h4>Professionalism</h4>\r\nCreative problem solver, precise technical ability, organized, goal oriented, excellent time management, inquisitive, fast learner with diverse creative experience, detail oriented, proficent writer, essential bookkeeping, and a very effective communicator.\r\n<h4>Applications</h4>\r\nAdobe Creative Suite CS6, Microsoft Office, Google Suite, AutoCAD, DSLR photography, video editing.\r\n<